node.title: Thunderstorm warning for Northland
node.description: Parts of Northland could be in for a stormy afternoon.
node.content:
["Parts of Northland could be in for a stormy afternoon.", "", "
\nPhoto: Twitter / @MetService\n
", "MetService has issued a severe thunderstorm watch for inland and western parts of the region, south of Kaitaia.", "It said scattered thunderstorms with localised heavy rain are expected between 4 and 9pm.", "The storm could cause surface or flash flooding and slips, especially near streams, rivers or narrow valleys.", "Driving conditions will be hazardous, MetService warned."]
